query:
SELECT 
  p.id, 
  p.stockUserId, 
  s.name as stockUserName,
  p.userId, 
  u.username,
  p.startAmount, 
  p.profitPercentage,
  p.createdAt
FROM stockUserPermissions p
JOIN users u ON p.userId = u.id
JOIN stockUsers s ON p.stockUserId = s.id
WHERE p.startAmount IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY p.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
